content: back in nyc, the vibes are unmatched 🔋✨ times square is buzzing like it never stopped. job's gone, but i'm here for a fresh start.
just turned 22 and feeling it, ya know? 🥳 took some time today to think about the past year, the mess-ups, the lessons. this year’s all about growth, refining my trading algos, and moving up 💪
so i've been knee-deep in AI market analysis stuff and it turns out my old method was kinda basic 😅 time to expand my mind a bit 🌍
